 (446,'Faculty of Humanities &amp; Social Sciences',5205,'Credits','Chairman: Dr. Maysoon Al-Nahar<br />\r\nEmail: maysnahar@index.com.jo<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe Department offers the Bachelor&#039;s and Master&#039;s programs in Archaeology.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAn M.A. program in Museology will be offered in the near future.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe Department houses the Archaeological Museum and the Folklore Museum. It provides training opportunities for students at Jordan&#039;s archaeological sites, like Khirbet Yajuz site, for instance. Many architectural features and artifacts are discovered during these excavations.<br />\r\n','info',1),
